---
// MediaDokumenter.astro
// Ganti VIDEO_ID dengan ID YouTube video dokumenter desa yang sebenarnya
const VIDEO_ID = "GEC6I2wmTg4"; // placeholder – ganti dengan ID YouTube asli
---

<!-- Wave Divider (from Hero/PetaKelurahan to MediaDokumenter) -->
<div class="wave-divider-media" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 70" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <path d="M0,40 C360,0 720,70 1080,30 C1260,10 1380,50 1440,40 L1440,70 L0,70 Z" fill="#0a1a0d"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<section class="section-media" id="media" aria-labelledby="media-title">

  <!-- Cinematic background particles -->
  <div class="media-particles" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="media-orb media-orb-1"></div>
    <div class="media-orb media-orb-2"></div>
    <div class="media-orb media-orb-3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:2;">

    <!-- Section Header -->
    <header class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-dark">🎬 Dokumenter & Media</span>
      <h2 class="section-title section-title-light" id="media-title">
        Cerita dari Lereng <span class="gradient-gold">Gunung Dempo</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-desc section-desc-light">
        Saksikan progress proker kami untuk masyarakat Kelurahan Gunung Dempo — Video dokumenter yang dibuat oleh tim KKNT 103 Kelompok 25 Universitas Sriwijaya.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Main video + sidebar highlights -->
    <div class="media-layout reveal reveal-delay-1">

      <!-- ===== LEFT: Main Video Player ===== -->
      <div class="media-video-col">
        <div class="video-wrapper" id="video-wrapper">
          <!-- Thumbnail overlay (click to play) -->
          <div class="video-thumbnail" id="video-thumbnail" role="button" tabindex="0"
               aria-label="Putar video dokumenter Kelurahan Gunung Dempo">
            <img
              src={`https://img.youtube.com/vi/${VIDEO_ID}/maxresdefault.jpg`}
              alt="Thumbnail dokumenter Kelurahan Gunung Dempo"
              class="video-thumb-img"
              width="1280"
              height="720"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <!-- Overlay gradient -->
            <div class="video-thumb-overlay"></div>
            <!-- Play button -->
            <div class="play-btn" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="play-icon">▶</div>
              <div class="play-ripple"></div>
              <div class="play-ripple play-ripple-2"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Bottom metadata -->
            <div class="video-meta">
              <span class="video-label">🎬 Dokumenter Progress</span>
              <span class="video-duration">Tonton Sekarang</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Actual iframe (hidden until click) -->
          <iframe
            id="yt-iframe"
            class="video-iframe"
            width="100%"
            height="100%"
            src=""
            data-src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${VIDEO_ID}?autoplay=1&rel=0&modestbranding=1`}
            title="Dokumenter Kelurahan Gunung Dempo"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
            aria-label="Video dokumenter Kelurahan Gunung Dempo"
          ></iframe>
        </div>

        <!-- Video caption bar -->
        <div class="video-caption-bar">
          <div class="vcb-info">
            <span class="vcb-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏔️</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="vcb-title">Kelurahan Gunung Dempo</strong>
              <span class="vcb-sub">Kota Pagar Alam, Sumatera Selatan</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href={`https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=${VIDEO_ID}`}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="vcb-yt-btn"
            id="btn-yt-external"
            aria-label="Buka di YouTube"
          >
            <svg width="20" height="14" viewBox="0 0 20 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M19.582 2.186a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-1.76-1.768C16.254 0 10 0 10 0S3.746 0 2.178.418A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 .418 2.186C0 3.763 0 7 0 7s0 3.237.418 4.814a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 1.76 1.768C3.746 14 10 14 10 14s6.254 0 7.822-.418a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 1.76-1.768C20 10.237 20 7 20 7s0-3.237-.418-4.814zM8 10V4l5.196 3L8 10z" fill="#fff"/>
            </svg>
            Buka di YouTube
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ===== RIGHT: Story Highlights ===== -->
      <aside class="media-sidebar" aria-label="Sorotan cerita desa">
        <h3 class="sidebar-title">✨ Sorotan Cerita</h3>

        <div class="story-cards">

          <article class="story-card reveal reveal-delay-2" id="story-kopi">
            <div class="story-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">☕</div>
            <div class="story-card-body">
              <h4 class="story-card-title">Kopi & Teh Lereng Dempo</h4>
              <p class="story-card-desc">
                Perjalanan petani lokal merawat tanaman kopi robusta dan teh
                premium di ketinggian 1.000–1.600 mdpl.
              </p>
              <span class="story-tag">🌿 Pertanian</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="story-card reveal reveal-delay-4" id="story-gotong">
            <div class="story-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🤝</div>
            <div class="story-card-body">
              <h4 class="story-card-title">Semangat Gotong Royong</h4>
              <p class="story-card-desc">
                Komunitas warga yang solid membangun desa bebas stunting
                bersama tim KKNT Universitas Sriwijaya.
              </p>
              <span class="story-tag">🏘️ Komunitas</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="story-card reveal reveal-delay-5" id="story-alam">
            <div class="story-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">🏔️</div>
            <div class="story-card-body">
              <h4 class="story-card-title">Keindahan Alam Gunung Dempo</h4>
              <p class="story-card-desc">
                Panorama gunung berapi aktif, hamparan kebun teh hijau, dan
                udara segar yang memikat setiap pengunjung.
              </p>
              <span class="story-tag">🌄 Wisata</span>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Wave out to next section -->
<div class="wave-divider-media-out" aria-hidden="true">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
    <path d="M0,30 C360,60 720,0 1080,40 C1260,55 1380,20 1440,30 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#ffffff"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<script>
  /* -------- YouTube Click-to-Play -------- */
  const thumbnail = document.getElementById('video-thumbnail');
  const iframe    = document.getElementById('yt-iframe') as HTMLIFrameElement | null;

  function activateVideo() {
    if (!thumbnail || !iframe) return;
    iframe.src = iframe.dataset.src ?? '';
    thumbnail.style.opacity    = '0';
    thumbnail.style.pointerEvents = 'none';
    setTimeout(() => { thumbnail.style.display = 'none'; }, 400);
    iframe.style.opacity = '1';
  }

  thumbnail?.addEventListener('click', activateVideo);
  thumbnail?.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    if ((e as KeyboardEvent).key === 'Enter' || (e as KeyboardEvent).key === ' ') {
      e.preventDefault();
      activateVideo();
    }
  });

  /* -------- Scroll Reveal -------- */
  const revealEls = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  const revealObs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(en => { if (en.isIntersecting) en.target.classList.add('visible'); });
  }, { threshold: 0.12 });
  revealEls.forEach(el => revealObs.observe(el));
</script>

<style>
  /* =========================================================
     MEDIA DOKUMENTER SECTION
  ========================================================= */

  /* Wave in */
  .wave-divider-media {
    display: block;
    line-height: 0;
    background: var(--clr-mist);
  }
  .wave-divider-media svg { width: 100%; display: block; }

  /* Wave out */
  .wave-divider-media-out {
    display: block;
    line-height: 0;
    background: #0a1a0d;
  }
  .wave-divider-media-out svg { width: 100%; display: block; }

  /* ===== Section base ===== */
  .section-media {
    background: #0a1a0d;
    position: relative;
    padding-block: var(--space-5xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Orb particles */
  .media-particles { position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1; }
  .media-orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(80px);
    opacity: 0.25;
    animation: floatSlow 12s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .media-orb-1 { width: 400px; height: 400px; top: -100px; left: -100px; background: radial-gradient(circle, #047857, transparent); }
  .media-orb-2 { width: 300px; height: 300px; bottom: -80px; right: 10%; background: radial-gradient(circle, #c47f3e, transparent); animation-delay: -4s; }
  .media-orb-3 { width: 250px; height: 250px; top: 40%; left: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, #10b981, transparent); animation-delay: -8s; opacity: 0.12; }

  /* ===== Header ===== */
  .section-title-light { color: #fff !important; }
  .section-desc-light  { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65) !important; }

  .eyebrow-dark {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15) !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.30);
    color: #34d399 !important;
  }

  .gradient-gold {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6c90e, #e8a43c, #d4975a) !important;
    -webkit-background-clip: text !important;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent !important;
    background-clip: text !important;
  }

  /* ===== Layout ===== */
  .media-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ===== Video wrapper ===== */
  .media-video-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md); }

  .video-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 0 0 1px rgba(16,185,129,0.15);
    background: #000;
  }

  /* Thumbnail */
  .video-thumbnail {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 2;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
  }
  .video-thumb-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .video-thumbnail:hover .video-thumb-img { transform: scale(1.04); }

  .video-thumb-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to top,
      rgba(5,46,22,0.85) 0%,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.20) 50%,
      rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 100%
    );
  }

  /* Play button */
  .play-btn {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .play-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clr-emerald-500), var(--clr-emerald-700));
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(16,185,129,0.5);
    transition: transform var(--transition-bounce), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding-left: 6px; /* optical centering of ▶ */
  }
  .video-thumbnail:hover .play-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 50px rgba(16,185,129,0.65);
  }

  /* Ripple rings */
  .play-ripple {
    position: absolute;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.4);
    animation: rippleOut 2s ease-out infinite;
  }
  .play-ripple-2 { animation-delay: 1s; }

  @keyframes rippleOut {
    0%   { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
    100% { transform: scale(2.2); opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Video bottom meta */
  .video-meta {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: var(--space-lg);
    left: var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    z-index: 3;
  }
  .video-label {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .video-duration {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Iframe */
  .video-iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border: none;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
    z-index: 1;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  }

  /* Caption bar */
  .video-caption-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }
  .vcb-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }
  .vcb-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .vcb-title {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .vcb-sub {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  }
  .vcb-yt-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: #FF0000;
    color: white;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    white-space: nowrap;
    transition: transform var(--transition-bounce), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(255,0,0,0.35);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .vcb-yt-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(255,0,0,0.5);
  }

  /* ===== Sidebar ===== */
  .media-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md); }

  .sidebar-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }

  .story-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-sm); }

  .story-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    cursor: default;
    transition: background var(--transition-base), border-color var(--transition-base), transform var(--transition-bounce);
  }
  .story-card:hover {
    background: rgba(16,185,129,0.10);
    border-color: rgba(16,185,129,0.28);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .story-card-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(16,185,129,0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .story-card-body { flex: 1; }
  .story-card-title {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .story-card-desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .story-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--clr-emerald-400);
    background: rgba(16,185,129,0.12);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  /* ===== Stats strip ===== */
  .media-stats-strip {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0;
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .mss-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-2xl);
    flex: 1;
    transition: background var(--transition-base);
  }
  .mss-item:hover { background: rgba(16,185,129,0.08); }
  .mss-num {
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--clr-emerald-400);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .mss-label {
    font-size: 0.73rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .mss-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .media-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .media-sidebar {
      order: 2;
    }
    .story-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .story-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .media-stats-strip {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    }
    .mss-item { flex: 0 0 50%; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .mss-divider { display: none; }
    .video-caption-bar { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
  }
</style>
